about Santa Claus?

166
00:07:27,017 --> 00:07:28,751
How awesome it was?

167
00:07:28,819 --> 00:07:30,386
Christmas was the highlight
of the year.

168
00:07:30,454 --> 00:07:32,188
Why wouldn't you want to keep
someone's world

169
00:07:32,256 --> 00:07:34,490
