I want bling. I can't be any
more specific than that.

192
00:08:33,832 --> 00:08:35,132
Okay, wait, hold up.

193
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,885
Please tell me that is a roll
of Certs in your pocket.

194
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:39,637
