for stretch marks?

195
00:08:39,704 --> 00:08:40,938
ChapStick. Lots of ChapStick.

196
00:08:41,006 --> 00:08:43,541
I want Channing Tatum
to stop being in stuff.

197
00:08:43,609 --> 00:08:45,042
When does Asian Santa arrive?

198
00:08:45,053 --> 00:08:45,992
Next.

199
00:08:47,512 --> 00:08:49,847
Just know, you have rights.

200
00:08:49,915 --> 00:08:50,932
