224
00:10:05,090 --> 00:10:08,092
Being a Jew, I generally
don't give Christmas gifts,

225
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:10,177
but considering how much you
care about the holiday

226
00:10:10,262 --> 00:10:13,631
